Steps you to INSTALL SASS

# Step 1: Make sure Node.js and npm are installed or updated
node -v
npm -v

# Step 2: create a new directory for your SASS/SCSS task
mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
cd 0x03-sass_scss

# Step 3: Install Sass (latest version) inside the new directory
npm install -g sass

# Step 4: Confirm Sass is installed
sass --version

